WEBVTT

01:52.020 --> 01:57.610
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.479 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 34]

02:06.430 --> 02:07.950
I won't hurt you as long

02:08.870 --> 02:10.150
as you do what I say.

02:12.470 --> 02:13.030
Go now.

02:19.280 --> 02:20.280
Fourth Lady?

02:22.190 --> 02:23.990
Sorry to have startled you, My Lady.

02:23.990 --> 02:24.750
However,

02:24.770 --> 02:27.120
the Residence has been full of guests
coming
and going lately.

02:27.120 --> 02:29.470
Please do not wander around, My Lady,

02:29.490 --> 02:30.930
in case you might be disturbed.

02:30.930 --> 02:31.640
I see.

02:31.660 --> 02:32.660
You may leave now.

02:32.730 --> 02:33.270
Understood.

02:33.270 --> 02:34.530
Pardon my offense, My Lady.

02:34.530 --> 02:35.610
I'll take my leave.

02:35.640 --> 02:36.329
Let's go.

02:46.200 --> 02:48.600
You are the Fourth Lady
of the Zheng family?

02:53.630 --> 02:54.470
Can you return

02:54.850 --> 02:56.450
that forehead band to me now?

02:59.200 --> 02:59.750
I...

03:00.560 --> 03:02.770
The Zheng family took something
they shouldn't have.

03:02.770 --> 03:04.170
I just want to get it back.

03:10.190 --> 03:10.870
Thank you.

03:11.960 --> 03:12.750
Gan Jiang.

03:14.560 --> 03:15.750
You know this sword?

03:17.400 --> 03:18.560
You are a Qi

03:19.030 --> 03:19.960
and an official?

03:22.240 --> 03:23.170
I'm not a bad guy.

03:24.340 --> 03:26.520
It's just that your eldest brother
committed evil deeds,

03:26.520 --> 03:27.480
so I...

03:27.980 --> 03:29.400
As reckless as my eldest brother is,

03:29.400 --> 03:31.930
he will ruin the Zheng family
sooner or later.

03:33.120 --> 03:34.490
Thank you for your help today.

03:34.490 --> 03:36.090
I'll surely repay this favor

03:36.120 --> 03:37.980
if there is a chance in the future.

04:09.760 --> 04:12.830
The female dancer
has performed one song after another.

04:12.830 --> 04:14.650
The Zheng family has made it so grand—

04:14.650 --> 04:15.880
I really feel

04:15.910 --> 04:17.190
flattered.

04:17.610 --> 04:18.720
Yet you haven't had

04:18.829 --> 04:20.000
a single sip of wine.

04:23.300 --> 04:24.900
If you have something to say,

04:25.070 --> 04:27.800
just cut to the chase,
Eldest Young Master Zheng.

04:27.800 --> 04:30.120
Today, I'd like to take the opportunity
of this welcome banquet

04:30.120 --> 04:31.470
to apologize to you.

04:31.570 --> 04:33.240
I was way too cautious before

04:33.390 --> 04:35.180
and mistook you, Gate Cdr. Fan,
for a bad person.

04:35.180 --> 04:36.440
If I ever offended you,

04:36.680 --> 04:37.740
please forgive me.

04:38.310 --> 04:39.360
From now on,

04:39.909 --> 04:41.570
we'll rely on you for the glory

04:42.000 --> 04:43.270
of the Zheng family.

04:47.060 --> 04:48.500
I'm flattered.

04:49.590 --> 04:51.170
Eldest Young Master, I hope you will

04:51.170 --> 04:54.370
attend the future
gate commander inauguration ceremony

04:55.040 --> 04:56.440
and give me more support.

04:56.870 --> 04:57.440
Okay.

05:02.310 --> 05:04.560
Gate Cdr. Fan,
you really are a remarkable woman,

05:04.560 --> 05:06.890
worthy of being personally picked
by the Governor.

05:06.890 --> 05:08.550
Thank you for the compliment.

05:09.050 --> 05:10.310
This time, let me toast

05:10.830 --> 05:12.760
to you, Eldest Young Master Zheng.

05:19.570 --> 05:20.840
Stop there!

05:21.720 --> 05:22.430
Freeze!

05:22.430 --> 05:23.390
Stop there!

05:24.390 --> 05:25.640
Don't run!

05:25.920 --> 05:27.040
Stop there!

05:27.690 --> 05:28.450
This way!

05:28.480 --> 05:29.610
Go after him! Hurry!

05:29.710 --> 05:30.680
Stop running!

05:31.830 --> 05:32.540
Come on.

05:41.240 --> 05:42.120
Gate Cdr. Fan

05:42.320 --> 05:44.040
brought someone else with her,

05:44.040 --> 05:45.970
and he is right in the backyard now.

05:46.200 --> 05:47.130
Catch him alive.

05:49.380 --> 05:50.350
How dare you.

05:51.600 --> 05:52.480
Hasn't my third brother

05:52.480 --> 05:54.560
always been in charge of transportation?

05:54.560 --> 05:55.390
What is he trying to do

05:55.390 --> 05:56.390
bringing it home?

05:56.480 --> 05:57.480
How about we

05:57.500 --> 05:59.390
go ask the Third Young Master about it?

05:59.390 --> 06:00.190
Don't bother.

06:00.560 --> 06:01.550
Just lock him up

06:02.310 --> 06:04.040
and let him reflect on himself.

06:09.480 --> 06:11.010
Eldest Young Master Zheng,

06:11.090 --> 06:13.070
do you have any urgent matters
to handle today?

06:13.070 --> 06:14.190
How about

06:14.210 --> 06:15.620
we meet another day?

06:17.610 --> 06:20.610
I thought you came here alone this time,
Gate Cdr. Fan.

06:20.720 --> 06:23.320
I didn't expect you
to leave a guest in the yard.

06:24.720 --> 06:26.240
What do you mean by that,

06:26.890 --> 06:28.420
Eldest Young Master Zheng?

06:28.750 --> 06:30.810
You are the heiress of the Fan family,

06:31.430 --> 06:33.750
and I am the eldest young master
of the Zheng family.

06:33.750 --> 06:35.040
We are a perfect match.

06:35.040 --> 06:36.680
If you marry me,

06:37.000 --> 06:38.560
your friend will also be my friend,

06:38.560 --> 06:40.690
and I will certainly not mistreat him.

06:41.870 --> 06:44.690
That's a rather novel idea,
Eldest Young Master Zheng.

06:44.690 --> 06:46.810
Don't you care about

06:48.270 --> 06:49.870
your brotherhood at all?

06:51.730 --> 06:54.330
You're marrying
into the Zheng family anyway.

06:55.240 --> 06:57.120
Does it matter who you marry?

06:57.480 --> 06:58.600
What if

06:59.190 --> 07:00.160
I don't want to?

07:02.060 --> 07:03.380
This matter is

07:04.800 --> 07:06.480
not up to you.

07:17.170 --> 07:18.850
The female dancer's sleeves

07:19.420 --> 07:20.930
had knockout drops on them.

07:20.930 --> 07:22.590
The heiress of the Fan family,

07:22.760 --> 07:25.020
and also the Gate Commander of Jing City.

07:25.320 --> 07:26.370
If I marry you,

07:26.710 --> 07:28.930
I can not only control the whole Jing City

07:28.930 --> 07:31.130
but also have the Fan family's support.

07:31.220 --> 07:33.690
Let's just make it a done deal today.

07:34.100 --> 07:35.300
I guess the Fan family

07:35.320 --> 07:38.720
won't refuse to acknowledge me
as their young lady's husband.

07:38.720 --> 07:39.520
Shameless...

08:00.360 --> 08:02.090
Stop running! Stop there!

08:12.430 --> 08:13.510
Stop.

08:26.680 --> 08:28.090
What did you do to Fan Yun?

08:28.240 --> 08:29.270
Don't worry.

08:29.600 --> 08:31.110
The Gate Commander will soon be

08:31.110 --> 08:32.580
part of the Zheng family.

08:32.990 --> 08:33.940
I'm afraid

08:33.960 --> 08:35.820
you'll have to bear with it today.

08:36.080 --> 08:36.750
Get him.

08:45.100 --> 08:46.270
Gate Commander,

08:48.030 --> 08:50.550
you look really charming today.

08:51.200 --> 08:52.130
What do you think

08:52.850 --> 08:53.890
people will

08:55.270 --> 08:57.200
say about us after today?

08:58.000 --> 09:01.400
I played the host and invited
the Gate Commander to a banquet.

09:02.120 --> 09:03.300
After a few rounds of drinks,

09:03.300 --> 09:06.160
we had a great time chatting
and fell for each other.

09:06.910 --> 09:09.040
It can be considered an amazing story.

09:10.010 --> 09:11.540
Eldest Young Master Zheng,

09:11.840 --> 09:12.440
you...

09:14.580 --> 09:16.180
Come a bit closer.

09:21.120 --> 09:21.870
Well,

09:22.400 --> 09:24.330
keep dreaming.

09:29.390 --> 09:30.240
Let go!

09:30.370 --> 09:31.850
Then I'll just dream on.

09:35.510 --> 09:36.510
Stay away from me!

09:37.030 --> 09:39.150
Let me go! Let go of me!

09:39.680 --> 09:40.730
Let me go!

09:44.710 --> 09:46.240
Second Young Master Zheng.

09:48.720 --> 09:50.780
Zheng the Second! What are you doing?

09:52.510 --> 09:54.510
How dare you lay a finger on my woman?

09:55.840 --> 09:57.840
You two are not married yet, are you?

09:58.030 --> 09:59.560
Then it just doesn't count.

10:00.770 --> 10:01.650
Jin,

10:02.560 --> 10:03.730
if you want to die,

10:04.520 --> 10:06.580
I can personally grant you your wish.

10:08.790 --> 10:10.120
You're threatening me?

10:12.200 --> 10:13.200
Guards!

10:27.210 --> 10:28.410
What do you want to do?

10:31.610 --> 10:32.700
Listen,

10:33.000 --> 10:34.480
if you dare to lay a finger on me,

10:34.480 --> 10:35.750
the Zhengs and our grandfather

10:35.750 --> 10:37.080
will never let you go.

10:40.850 --> 10:42.090
If you kill me,

10:42.910 --> 10:44.660
you will be committing fratricide,

10:44.660 --> 10:48.060
and you won't be able to become
the Master of the Zheng family.

10:57.700 --> 10:58.540
I was wrong!

11:04.510 --> 11:05.630
I'm sorry.

11:06.720 --> 11:07.650
I'm begging you.

11:08.750 --> 11:09.950
Please don't kill me.

11:11.670 --> 11:12.550
Jin,

11:13.920 --> 11:16.050
it's good that you know you were wrong.

11:41.240 --> 11:42.270
No...

11:42.600 --> 11:43.790
Go away.

11:44.480 --> 11:45.410
Don't come over.

11:46.520 --> 11:47.670
Go away.

11:50.200 --> 11:51.200
Stay away from me.

11:51.570 --> 11:53.940
Don't come over. Don't...

11:54.120 --> 11:56.200
Don't. Go away!

11:57.390 --> 11:58.390
Don't be afraid.

11:58.410 --> 11:59.340
It's me.

12:04.510 --> 12:05.150
Zheng...

12:06.070 --> 12:07.600
Second Young Master Zheng.

12:19.170 --> 12:21.030
The effects of the drug
haven't worn off yet.

12:21.030 --> 12:22.160
Don't move too much.

12:27.410 --> 12:28.580
It's all thanks

12:29.480 --> 12:30.540
to your help today.

12:31.580 --> 12:32.550
Thank you,

12:32.580 --> 12:34.110
Second Young Master Zheng.

12:36.250 --> 12:38.170
Zheng Jin used an anesthetic,

12:38.360 --> 12:39.360
but essentially,

12:39.360 --> 12:41.760
it is more harmful than other anesthetics.

12:42.270 --> 12:43.150
Therefore,

12:43.170 --> 12:45.100
you need plenty of rest to recover.

12:46.960 --> 12:47.670
No way.

12:48.630 --> 12:49.790
I must go back.

12:51.780 --> 12:52.660
Why?

12:52.680 --> 12:53.340
Because...

12:55.320 --> 12:55.980
Because...

12:57.000 --> 12:57.910
Because...

12:59.840 --> 13:00.870
Because Gao Ran is

13:01.310 --> 13:02.650
still waiting for me.

13:05.760 --> 13:08.090
It's actually because of Qi Zheng, right?

13:12.440 --> 13:13.610
H-How...

13:14.720 --> 13:16.120
How did you know?

13:18.750 --> 13:19.390
Wait...

13:21.510 --> 13:22.930
What happened to Qi Zheng?

13:22.930 --> 13:24.480
Is he in danger?

13:47.820 --> 13:49.100
Where am I?

13:52.360 --> 13:53.600
What is this place?

13:54.790 --> 13:56.790
This is the Zheng family's dungeon.

13:57.960 --> 13:59.320
Who's talking?

14:05.910 --> 14:06.870
Who are you?

14:08.720 --> 14:10.450
Come here and get me out of here.

14:10.560 --> 14:11.280
Come here.

14:21.050 --> 14:24.450
You're the dignified Third Young Master
of the Zheng family.

14:25.630 --> 14:27.630
How come you are also locked up here?

14:27.890 --> 14:30.420
You don't need to treat me
with that attitude.

14:30.640 --> 14:31.560
I am

14:31.580 --> 14:33.420
the Third Young Master
of the Zheng family,

14:33.420 --> 14:35.870
but I have no interest
in being the clan leader.

14:35.870 --> 14:37.240
Nor do I harbor any animosity

14:37.240 --> 14:38.470
towards Gate Cdr. Fan.

14:38.470 --> 14:39.930
Me ending up locked up here

14:40.200 --> 14:41.480
is purely bad luck.

14:43.870 --> 14:45.150
In this case,

14:45.150 --> 14:46.680
why don't you find a way out?

14:48.600 --> 14:49.930
Don't worry about that.

14:50.600 --> 14:52.670
As smart as my fourth sister is,

14:52.670 --> 14:54.630
she will definitely find this place soon

14:54.630 --> 14:55.870
and get me out of here.

14:57.080 --> 14:58.010
The Fourth Lady?

15:00.360 --> 15:01.890
Second Young Master Zheng,

15:02.000 --> 15:03.340
please let me out.

15:04.030 --> 15:04.950
To me,

15:05.360 --> 15:07.200
nothing matters more than your safety.

15:07.200 --> 15:08.930
I don't care about anyone else.

15:12.670 --> 15:13.600
We will have

15:14.080 --> 15:15.340
our wedding very soon.

15:15.870 --> 15:17.390
As long as you stay and live here,

15:17.390 --> 15:19.340
I will prepare whatever you need.

15:20.030 --> 15:22.390
Everything can wait
until after the wedding.

15:22.390 --> 15:23.920
What are you talking about?

15:24.960 --> 15:26.270
Didn't you tell me that

15:26.600 --> 15:28.000
after I entered the city,

15:28.240 --> 15:29.680
you would never force me?

15:33.000 --> 15:34.720
Don't look so down.

15:34.750 --> 15:36.630
You need to rest well and heal now.

15:36.750 --> 15:37.790
Once you have fully recovered,

15:37.790 --> 15:39.320
you can walk around as you please,

15:39.320 --> 15:41.380
as long as you don't leave this place.

15:45.510 --> 15:46.440
Zheng Shi,

15:47.310 --> 15:49.240
are you trying to put me
under house arrest?

15:49.240 --> 15:50.370
I am protecting you.

15:53.350 --> 15:55.030
I really misjudged you.

15:55.050 --> 15:56.650
Zheng Shi, you...

15:58.390 --> 16:00.390
It's weird now that I think about it.

16:00.550 --> 16:01.790
Looking closely,

16:02.490 --> 16:04.490
there is nothing special about you.

16:07.480 --> 16:08.630
You are so ordinary,

16:09.440 --> 16:10.850
yet I'm still so into you.

16:12.120 --> 16:13.240
What I have

16:13.260 --> 16:14.410
must be true love.

16:18.150 --> 16:19.910
Do you have to keep me here?

16:26.000 --> 16:28.200
But why is true love so bitter?

16:31.910 --> 16:33.780
If only love in this world could

16:34.440 --> 16:36.700
always turn out the way people want it to.

16:41.270 --> 16:43.390
Do you listen to me?

16:46.260 --> 16:47.990
Do you care about him that much?

16:51.090 --> 16:51.930
Yes.

16:58.140 --> 16:59.800
I'll go deal with his problem.

17:33.030 --> 17:34.590
She climbed the tree to pick flowers

17:34.590 --> 17:36.440
and tried to shoo away
the birds on the tree.

17:36.440 --> 17:38.770
Yet she accidentally fell into the water.

17:41.030 --> 17:42.100
Silly girl.

17:43.880 --> 17:45.480
Have you called any physicians
to check in on her?

17:45.480 --> 17:47.030
She insisted it wasn't necessary.

17:47.030 --> 17:47.960
But fortunately, it's just a cold.

17:47.960 --> 17:49.420
There's nothing serious.

17:49.510 --> 17:50.440
It's just that

17:51.280 --> 17:52.580
she kept mumbling your name

17:52.580 --> 17:54.140
even in her sleep.

18:07.380 --> 18:07.950
Wei Ying.

18:09.030 --> 18:09.720
Wei Ying!

18:11.790 --> 18:12.830
Did you notice?

18:15.030 --> 18:16.160
Yeah, I did.

19:06.850 --> 19:07.880
You're awake.

19:10.170 --> 19:11.220
You're here.

19:14.230 --> 19:16.490
Why do you always pick on those two birds?

19:18.570 --> 19:20.290
They treat love like a game.

19:20.660 --> 19:21.520
I don't like it.

19:22.750 --> 19:23.790
How is it a game?

19:25.220 --> 19:26.960
They fly here for a moment,

19:27.370 --> 19:28.530
and then there.

19:28.800 --> 19:31.200
They never want to stay
on one tree for long.

19:34.830 --> 19:36.900
That's because you don't know them well,

19:36.900 --> 19:38.500
and you misunderstand them.

19:43.710 --> 19:45.470
But they always fly so high.

19:46.040 --> 19:48.500
How am I supposed to get a chance
to know them?

20:02.950 --> 20:04.120
Maybe

20:04.770 --> 20:06.500
they have already realized it.

20:09.070 --> 20:10.420
They might have found

20:11.240 --> 20:13.440
the tree where they want to build a nest,

20:13.590 --> 20:15.450
but they've never dared to say it.

20:24.750 --> 20:25.640
This is

20:26.180 --> 20:27.940
a sachet I made

20:27.970 --> 20:29.280
using a recipe I asked around for.

20:29.280 --> 20:30.170
Wear it

20:30.530 --> 20:31.720
to prevent a rash.

20:45.480 --> 20:46.680
You do care so much

20:47.400 --> 20:48.590
about the Governor.

20:50.610 --> 20:51.400
Very well.

21:09.340 --> 21:12.040
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

21:11.400 --> 21:13.080
I am not that bird.

21:12.070 --> 21:13.280
♪ Over the whole town ♪

21:13.100 --> 21:14.690
I only care about one person.

21:13.310 --> 21:15.810
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

21:15.950 --> 21:19.520
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

21:22.270 --> 21:24.740
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

21:24.770 --> 21:26.130
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

21:26.150 --> 21:29.040
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

21:29.070 --> 21:32.540
♪ Strike out
on a fearless dream's frontier ♪

21:33.950 --> 21:37.290
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

21:37.350 --> 21:40.380
♪ A wisp of softness
tints your brow each day ♪

21:40.400 --> 21:42.400
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

21:42.420 --> 21:45.540
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

21:45.570 --> 21:47.570
♪ We'll ride the ups and downs ♪

21:47.590 --> 21:50.020
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

21:50.260 --> 21:53.280
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

21:53.410 --> 21:58.210
♪ Wander together through wind and frost ♪

21:58.240 --> 22:00.240
♪ Every dark night fades at last ♪

22:00.270 --> 22:02.790
♪ When fate resides within our sight ♪

22:02.900 --> 22:07.590
♪ Gazing toward each other's
distant light ♪

22:07.690 --> 22:11.110
♪ What do heaven and earth seek
but salvation in companionship? ♪

22:11.140 --> 22:12.760
♪ Don't let the sun down ♪

22:12.820 --> 22:15.250
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

22:15.490 --> 22:18.510
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

22:18.630 --> 22:23.440
♪ Wander together through wind and frost ♪

22:23.470 --> 22:25.470
♪ Every dark night fades at last ♪

22:25.490 --> 22:28.020
♪ When fate resides within our sight ♪

22:28.130 --> 22:32.810
♪ Gazing toward each other's
distant light ♪

22:32.910 --> 22:36.340
♪ What do heaven and earth seek
but salvation in companionship? ♪

22:36.360 --> 22:39.050
♪ Don't let the sun down ♪

23:00.550 --> 23:01.240
My Lady.

23:01.260 --> 23:02.670
W-What brings you here?

23:05.080 --> 23:06.640
Her Ladyship ignores everyone else

23:06.640 --> 23:08.050
except for those close to her.

23:08.050 --> 23:09.050
Oh, you're right.

23:09.310 --> 23:10.150
Fourth Lady,

23:10.170 --> 23:11.270
are you here looking

23:11.270 --> 23:12.800
for the Third Young Master?

23:13.310 --> 23:15.270
The Third Young Master has been missing
since yesterday.

23:15.270 --> 23:16.440
I couldn't find him either.

23:16.440 --> 23:18.160
I don't know where he went.

23:20.920 --> 23:21.550
Qi Zheng,

23:22.750 --> 23:24.440
please stay safe.

23:25.510 --> 23:26.440
Young Master Shi is not here.

23:26.440 --> 23:27.650
Please go back, My Lady...

23:27.650 --> 23:28.160
My Lady!

23:28.160 --> 23:29.090
Second Brother.

23:33.790 --> 23:34.440
You...

23:35.790 --> 23:36.830
And you are?

23:37.310 --> 23:38.720
This is our Fourth Lady.

23:39.410 --> 23:40.490
Fourth Lady Zheng.

23:43.030 --> 23:44.360
Second Sister-in-Law.

23:44.630 --> 23:46.970
The Mute Lady is quite talkative today.

23:51.880 --> 23:53.240
I'm not your second sister-in-law.

23:53.240 --> 23:53.810
I am...

23:54.750 --> 23:55.440
I...

23:57.530 --> 23:59.000
Anyway, I can't explain it

23:59.020 --> 24:00.420
clearly to you right now.

24:01.110 --> 24:03.310
But I'm not your second sister-in-law.

24:04.240 --> 24:05.770
Where is my second brother?

24:05.880 --> 24:07.410
He went to look for someone.

24:07.750 --> 24:11.160
Maybe he went to your eldest brother's place
to look for someone.

24:11.160 --> 24:11.780
Features.

24:12.240 --> 24:12.970
Features...

24:15.000 --> 24:16.460
Fourth Lady Zheng, are you

24:16.620 --> 24:18.620
going to help me look for him as well?

24:20.200 --> 24:21.030
He's about

24:21.530 --> 24:22.290
this tall,

24:22.680 --> 24:23.810
wearing a headband,

24:24.000 --> 24:25.200
and carrying a sword.

24:27.310 --> 24:28.240
Gan Jiang?

24:29.180 --> 24:29.830
Yep!

24:30.030 --> 24:31.430
It's the Gan Jiang Sword.

24:32.880 --> 24:35.340
Why is everyone
looking for someone lately?

24:35.530 --> 24:37.260
Why is everyone going missing?

24:37.480 --> 24:40.030
Even my third brother is
nowhere to be found.

24:41.750 --> 24:42.810
Fourth Lady Zheng?

24:44.510 --> 24:45.440
Follow me.

24:46.440 --> 24:47.270
Okay.

24:48.330 --> 24:49.640
Lady Fan Yun cannot leave here.

24:49.640 --> 24:50.200
This...

24:50.480 --> 24:51.680
This is also Young Master Shi's order.

24:51.680 --> 24:52.030
Yes.

24:52.410 --> 24:53.450
Are you sure?

25:01.200 --> 25:02.080
Looks like

25:02.350 --> 25:04.210
it's time for you to come in handy.

25:09.400 --> 25:10.900
If you release Gao Ran,

25:12.910 --> 25:14.910
this clan leader ring will be yours.

25:20.550 --> 25:21.860
Is Gao Ran so important

25:23.160 --> 25:25.090
that he's worth a clan leader ring?

25:26.760 --> 25:29.020
How do I know whether you're lying or not?

25:30.000 --> 25:30.860
And how do I know

25:31.350 --> 25:32.830
if this ring is real?

25:37.320 --> 25:38.300
If you don't believe me,

25:38.300 --> 25:39.700
you can simply refuse it.

25:40.030 --> 25:40.640
But I'm afraid

25:40.640 --> 25:43.040
you'll never have
another chance to get it.

25:47.790 --> 25:49.190
You're willing to give up

25:50.720 --> 25:53.350
such an important thing
just for an outsider?

25:57.960 --> 25:59.640
Only narrow-minded people

26:00.040 --> 26:01.170
care so much

26:01.340 --> 26:03.100
about insiders or outsiders.

26:04.440 --> 26:05.180
But I

26:06.260 --> 26:07.780
only care if it's worth it.

26:24.400 --> 26:25.260
Wait here.

26:42.720 --> 26:44.780
My eldest brother wants to catch you?

26:45.590 --> 26:46.590
So

26:46.590 --> 26:48.030
you must not
let your eldest brother find me,

26:48.030 --> 26:49.290
or I will be in trouble.

26:49.630 --> 26:51.020
Reckless and selfish.

26:53.550 --> 26:54.840
Now that Elder Zheng is gone,

26:54.840 --> 26:55.880
everyone is coveting

26:55.880 --> 26:57.480
the position of clan leader.

26:58.310 --> 26:59.110
A clan leader's position

26:59.110 --> 27:00.480
should be a burden to bear

27:00.480 --> 27:02.410
instead of something to fight for.

27:04.770 --> 27:05.760
Fourth Lady Zheng,

27:05.760 --> 27:07.390
where are we going now?

27:08.830 --> 27:09.430
The woodshed.

27:09.430 --> 27:10.340
The woodshed?

27:13.070 --> 27:14.510
Eldest Young Master, please.

27:14.510 --> 27:15.400
Watch your step.

27:15.400 --> 27:16.000
Slow down.

27:16.700 --> 27:17.480
Eldest Young Master,

27:17.480 --> 27:19.270
the two of them are being well-behaved

27:19.270 --> 27:21.600
and show no intentions
to get out of there.

27:21.830 --> 27:22.750
However,

27:24.100 --> 27:26.080
we're locking
the Third Young Master up here.

27:26.080 --> 27:27.620
If Master finds out about it,

27:27.620 --> 27:29.820
will he blame us?

27:32.030 --> 27:33.160
You talk too much.

27:33.330 --> 27:34.570
Yes.

27:34.590 --> 27:36.590
I shouldn't have spoken out of turn.

27:37.750 --> 27:39.590
I didn't expect you to be so important

27:39.590 --> 27:40.880
to Zheng the Second.

27:44.240 --> 27:45.720
You're lucky to have survived this time.

27:45.720 --> 27:47.640
If you fall into my hands again,

27:47.640 --> 27:49.570
things won't end this well for you.

27:50.070 --> 27:50.640
Tell me

27:50.640 --> 27:51.900
what you did to Fan Yun.

27:52.270 --> 27:54.770
Jin! Jin! Jin!

27:54.790 --> 27:55.550
Wait!

27:55.580 --> 27:57.110
You can't release him, Jin.

27:58.550 --> 27:59.640
You can't.

28:00.590 --> 28:02.190
Are you telling me what to do?

28:02.350 --> 28:03.280
I wouldn't dare.

28:03.680 --> 28:05.740
I just want to tell you what happened.

28:05.880 --> 28:08.130
You can make your decision
after hearing me out.

28:08.130 --> 28:10.060
You two-faced good-for-nothing.

28:10.920 --> 28:12.850
I don't want to talk to you anymore.

28:13.190 --> 28:14.590
Whatever you have to say,

28:15.190 --> 28:16.640
go tell Grandfather.

28:16.660 --> 28:19.420
Tell him yourself when he comes back.

28:20.750 --> 28:21.660
Jin,

28:22.030 --> 28:23.400
I know I was wrong.

28:23.750 --> 28:25.480
Please give me one more chance,

28:25.520 --> 28:26.440
okay?

28:28.030 --> 28:29.350
I'm begging you, Jin.

28:32.310 --> 28:33.110
Open the door.

28:33.420 --> 28:33.900
Yes.

28:33.930 --> 28:34.850
Thank you, Jin.

28:40.620 --> 28:41.620
What about me?

28:55.680 --> 28:57.120
The woodshed you mentioned

28:57.120 --> 28:58.540
could be used to lock people up?

28:58.540 --> 29:01.070
It's a disguise
for the underground dungeon.

29:02.070 --> 29:03.870
You wait here. I'll go handle it.

29:03.910 --> 29:04.850
Let me go with you.

29:04.850 --> 29:06.200
It'll be better if you stay here.

29:06.200 --> 29:07.060
Let me go alone.

29:10.590 --> 29:11.850
Let me take this chance

29:12.110 --> 29:13.840
to scope out this place as well.

29:24.310 --> 29:25.310
Thanks.

29:25.850 --> 29:27.190
I can't hold back anymore.

29:27.190 --> 29:28.470
Let me drink first.

29:46.040 --> 29:47.360
Where is my third brother?

29:47.360 --> 29:48.490
He was here just now.

29:48.630 --> 29:49.700
He hasn't come back

29:49.720 --> 29:51.380
since Zheng Jin took him away.

29:54.850 --> 29:56.310
Are you going to let me out?

30:06.200 --> 30:07.200
It's too dirty.

30:11.110 --> 30:12.070
Thank you.

30:12.850 --> 30:13.770
Take it off

30:13.790 --> 30:14.920
before you thank me.

30:37.560 --> 30:38.820
Where is the exit here?

30:42.300 --> 30:44.430
I'm leaving if you don't say anything.

30:47.070 --> 30:47.960
This way.

30:56.350 --> 30:57.550
The exit is over here.

30:58.000 --> 30:59.260
Then let's go this way.

31:52.480 --> 31:53.480
This is weird.

32:05.250 --> 32:06.700
It's empty inside here.

32:06.790 --> 32:08.250
There must be a mechanism.

32:08.340 --> 32:09.470
Let's look for it.

32:35.060 --> 32:37.060
So there really is a secret passage.

32:39.180 --> 32:40.260
How did you find it?

32:41.270 --> 32:42.030
I...

32:42.250 --> 32:43.930
I accidentally pressed it.

32:50.400 --> 32:53.000
How did you know
there is a secret passage here?

32:54.290 --> 32:56.750
If this private prison
only had one opening,

32:56.840 --> 32:59.000
the wind underground would always blow
from the southeast.

32:59.000 --> 33:00.200
But do you remember that?

33:00.200 --> 33:01.680
When the prison guards were
eating just now,

33:01.680 --> 33:03.880
their smoke blew to the southwest.

33:04.100 --> 33:05.430
This means there must be

33:05.640 --> 33:06.790
another passage on the other side

33:06.790 --> 33:07.790
to create a draft.

33:11.390 --> 33:13.120
Let's go inside and take a look.

34:07.630 --> 34:08.350
Gunpowder?

34:09.560 --> 34:11.620
There's gunpowder everywhere here.

34:12.190 --> 34:14.120
No wonder Liu Mu couldn't find any.

34:15.630 --> 34:16.560
That's strange.

34:17.159 --> 34:18.880
This doesn't make sense, though.

34:18.880 --> 34:21.260
Who would hide all this gunpowder
in their own house?

34:21.260 --> 34:22.699
Who would do such a thing?

34:25.030 --> 34:26.030
The Zheng family.

34:33.900 --> 34:35.150
Why did your third brother

34:35.150 --> 34:36.679
end up being locked up here?

34:38.710 --> 34:39.880
This is impossible.

34:43.840 --> 34:46.170
Now is not the time
to figure out the truth.

34:46.409 --> 34:47.960
We need to dispose of

34:48.170 --> 34:49.429
this gunpowder first.

34:49.929 --> 34:51.690
Otherwise, if anyone
uses them in the future,

34:51.690 --> 34:53.889
the consequences will be devastating.

34:54.150 --> 34:55.510
What do you want to do?

35:03.710 --> 35:05.210
Of course, it's to "cool down"

35:05.210 --> 35:06.610
this batch of gunpowder.

35:26.970 --> 35:28.300
Have some more.

35:28.800 --> 35:30.110
It's a long journey.

35:30.110 --> 35:31.770
You've all contributed a lot.

35:32.190 --> 35:32.840
Come on.

35:35.590 --> 35:36.360
Master.

35:37.330 --> 35:38.590
What's wrong, Master?

35:42.360 --> 35:43.890
I had sudden palpitations.

35:44.880 --> 35:46.540
I'm probably a bit exhausted.

35:46.930 --> 35:47.820
Why not

35:47.850 --> 35:49.330
go inside and take a rest?

35:51.160 --> 35:52.360
Let me just rest here.

36:20.550 --> 36:22.080
Second Young Master Zheng?

36:23.110 --> 36:24.440
What are you doing here?

36:28.520 --> 36:29.690
What...

36:29.710 --> 36:30.910
What happened to him?

36:30.920 --> 36:31.520
He...

36:32.650 --> 36:34.000
Who is there? Who?

36:35.600 --> 36:36.690
Come on, run.

36:37.800 --> 36:39.210
Second Young Master Zheng,

36:39.210 --> 36:40.610
what exactly is going on?

36:43.200 --> 36:44.220
It seems to be Young Master Shi.

36:44.220 --> 36:45.220
Young Master Shi?

36:49.250 --> 36:50.630
The Eldest Young Master was murdered!

36:50.630 --> 36:51.360
Young Master Shi

36:51.360 --> 36:53.170
killed the Eldest Young Master?

36:53.190 --> 36:53.980
Everyone,

36:54.010 --> 36:55.320
go after Young Master Shi!

36:55.320 --> 36:56.920
-Understood!
-Understood!

37:04.740 --> 37:05.870
Where is he? Get him!

37:10.600 --> 37:12.310
Why were you there?

37:12.560 --> 37:13.650
I didn't kill Jin.

37:14.030 --> 37:16.090
When I got there, he was already dead.

37:16.110 --> 37:17.550
Then why did you run?

37:18.030 --> 37:19.110
Why didn't you

37:19.110 --> 37:20.670
explain it to them just now?

37:21.450 --> 37:22.450
Do you believe me?

37:23.400 --> 37:24.320
Of course I do.

37:24.660 --> 37:25.850
Given your personality,

37:25.850 --> 37:26.830
if you killed someone,

37:26.830 --> 37:28.320
you'd definitely admit it.

37:28.320 --> 37:29.230
But just because I believe you,

37:29.230 --> 37:30.000
it doesn't mean that

37:30.000 --> 37:31.430
they will believe you, too.

37:31.430 --> 37:33.360
So why should I explain it to them?

37:33.480 --> 37:35.540
Your belief in me is all that matters.

37:36.050 --> 37:37.180
Who on earth

37:37.210 --> 37:38.560
killed Zheng Jin?

37:40.000 --> 37:40.880
I told him a long time ago

37:40.880 --> 37:42.360
not to be so full of himself.

37:42.360 --> 37:44.090
There are plenty of people
who want to kill him,

37:44.090 --> 37:45.520
but those who could do it
in the Zheng Residence

37:45.520 --> 37:46.850
are few and far between.

37:47.150 --> 37:48.550
So you mean it was someone

37:49.590 --> 37:50.850
from the Zheng family?

37:51.180 --> 37:52.750
If there's a traitor in the Zheng family,

37:52.750 --> 37:54.990
the truth will eventually come to light.

37:54.990 --> 37:56.640
Go back and stay with me.

37:56.660 --> 37:57.700
Don't run around.

38:05.700 --> 38:06.760
Fourth Lady Zheng,

38:07.300 --> 38:09.130
are there any carrier pigeons left
in the Residence?

38:09.130 --> 38:10.640
The Gate Commander Residence caught fire.

38:10.640 --> 38:12.640
I'm keeping those pigeons.

38:13.950 --> 38:14.950
I'll go get them.

38:15.720 --> 38:16.510
Thank you.

38:43.560 --> 38:44.620
Fourth Lady Zheng,

38:45.200 --> 38:47.470
please help me send this letter.

38:50.100 --> 38:50.700
By the way,

38:51.190 --> 38:52.840
you said when you came to save me,

38:52.840 --> 38:54.440
Fan Yun was waiting outside?

38:55.370 --> 38:58.100
Maybe she heard the commotion
and hid somewhere.

38:59.590 --> 39:01.450
It looks like I have to go find her.

39:03.050 --> 39:04.270
I promise I'll repay you

39:04.270 --> 39:05.530
for this favor one day.

39:08.870 --> 39:10.590
It's good that you owe me.

39:23.150 --> 39:24.550
Move over a bit.

39:25.830 --> 39:27.350
You can just ignore me.

39:33.690 --> 39:34.560
Why did you

39:35.150 --> 39:36.960
make yourself look like this?

39:37.690 --> 39:38.660
What do you know?

39:38.890 --> 39:40.280
As tall and mighty as I am,

39:40.280 --> 39:41.530
I would stand out too much over there.

39:41.530 --> 39:43.130
I can keep a low profile here.

39:43.560 --> 39:44.210
Hey.

39:45.260 --> 39:46.780
When necessary...

40:08.590 --> 40:09.280
Keep up!

40:20.210 --> 40:20.890
Who is it?

40:23.670 --> 40:24.600
Who's out there?

40:28.590 --> 40:29.240
Fan Yun.

40:29.260 --> 40:30.010
Qi Zheng.

40:32.020 --> 40:33.150
-Qi Zheng.
-Fan Yun.

40:33.740 --> 40:34.700
Are you okay?

40:34.730 --> 40:35.890
I'm fine.

40:35.910 --> 40:37.020
Great!

40:37.070 --> 40:38.400
I finally got to see you.

40:39.000 --> 40:40.260
How did you get in here?

40:40.840 --> 40:41.360
I...

40:43.480 --> 40:44.540
Fourth Lady Zheng.

40:45.340 --> 40:46.860
Alright, we should go now.

40:48.980 --> 40:50.180
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

40:53.920 --> 40:55.330
It really never ends.

40:55.350 --> 40:57.590
They won't let us rest
even in the middle of the night.

40:57.590 --> 40:58.400
Guys!

40:58.480 --> 40:59.110
Come on.

40:59.110 --> 41:00.150
Come and lend us a hand.

41:00.150 --> 41:01.080
Come on, help us.

41:01.630 --> 41:02.230
Be quick.

41:02.230 --> 41:03.110
Unload this one, and we can sleep.

41:03.110 --> 41:04.770
Wrap up early and sleep early.

41:06.050 --> 41:07.180
One, two.

41:07.210 --> 41:08.470
Slow down. Be careful.

41:10.510 --> 41:11.070
Well,

41:11.420 --> 41:12.460
don't you think

41:12.480 --> 41:15.000
this one is heavier
than all the previous ones?

41:15.000 --> 41:15.840
They're the same goods.

41:15.840 --> 41:16.920
What do you mean by "heavier"?

41:16.920 --> 41:18.110
I think you just want to slack off.

41:18.110 --> 41:19.190
Who wants to slack off?

41:19.190 --> 41:22.120
It's just that it takes a bit more effort
than before.

41:23.730 --> 41:25.720
So many weapons
have been delivered here recently.

41:25.720 --> 41:27.050
Is there going to be a war?

41:27.050 --> 41:28.110
Shut up. Don't ask.

41:28.480 --> 41:29.400
We do whatever

41:29.400 --> 41:30.510
the higher-ups tell us to do.

41:30.510 --> 41:32.440
Know less, and you can live longer.

41:33.230 --> 41:34.030
Push!

41:35.960 --> 41:36.920
It's finally done.

41:36.920 --> 41:37.590
Guys,

41:37.960 --> 41:38.850
let's go sleep.

42:16.390 --> 42:17.200
Be careful.

42:33.890 --> 42:35.080
Oh, my God.

42:35.730 --> 42:36.790
So much gunpowder.

42:38.800 --> 42:40.400
What are they planning to do?

42:46.620 --> 42:47.620
Master.

43:08.910 --> 43:10.030
Pack our things

43:10.350 --> 43:11.560
and head back to Jing City.

43:11.560 --> 43:12.290
Understood.

43:36.890 --> 43:39.550
Is this face really
worth looking at so closely?

43:39.650 --> 43:41.480
Appearance is nothing.

43:41.880 --> 43:42.990
For someone like me

43:43.010 --> 43:45.410
who can see the essence
beyond the surface,

43:45.410 --> 43:46.730
as long as you are in my heart,

43:46.730 --> 43:48.660
even a stone would remind me of you.

43:51.220 --> 43:52.960
With such beautiful dimples,

43:53.190 --> 43:55.120
you can only smile at me from now on.

44:00.860 --> 44:02.860
Your Excellency. Your Excellency.

44:03.400 --> 44:04.400
Your Excellency.

44:05.210 --> 44:06.210
Your Excellency.

44:09.750 --> 44:11.230
Did I see it or not?

44:11.250 --> 44:12.030
Before His Excellency left,

44:12.030 --> 44:13.610
he didn't tell us what we should do.

44:13.610 --> 44:15.160
If my sister finds out
that we've known it already,

44:15.160 --> 44:16.160
I'll be dead meat.

44:16.180 --> 44:17.370
It's your sister. You go handle it.

44:17.370 --> 44:18.530
You go. I'm not going.

44:18.530 --> 44:19.340
I'm not going.

44:23.740 --> 44:26.140
You two are being
a bit too loud, aren't you?

44:32.190 --> 44:33.550
-Your Excellency.
-Your Excellency.

44:33.550 --> 44:35.480
We have a weighty matter to report.

44:43.320 --> 44:44.250
Take a look at it.

44:47.900 --> 44:49.100
A hoard of munitions?

44:49.240 --> 44:49.840
What...

44:50.370 --> 44:52.280
No wonder Zheng Tao is so confident.

44:52.280 --> 44:53.540
With these munitions,

44:53.560 --> 44:54.480
the Zheng family really can

44:54.480 --> 44:55.880
either attack or defend.

44:56.000 --> 44:58.330
The Zheng family is truly
a nest of danger.

44:58.710 --> 45:01.440
Seems like Jing City
will be thrown into turmoil.

45:04.110 --> 45:04.920
Lord Wei,

45:05.590 --> 45:06.320
Lord Yan.

45:07.740 --> 45:08.400
-Yes.
-Yes.

45:09.710 --> 45:11.470
On behalf of the Governor, I'm ordering

45:11.470 --> 45:13.470
you two to lead the Qi family's army

45:13.490 --> 45:15.080
to Jing City immediately.

45:15.250 --> 45:16.470
Bring siege weapons

45:16.920 --> 45:19.140
and station outside Jing City on standby.

45:19.140 --> 45:20.750
Do not make any rash moves.

45:21.450 --> 45:22.730
Also, notify Lord Fan Qi.

45:22.730 --> 45:23.950
-We'll go get ready
-We'll go get ready

45:23.950 --> 45:26.080
-and set off today.
-and set off today.

45:26.320 --> 45:27.350
Faster.

45:27.790 --> 45:29.790
We must reach Jing City tonight!

45:51.040 --> 45:51.690
Master,

45:52.220 --> 45:53.750
according to the servants,

45:54.070 --> 45:56.110
when the Eldest Young Master was murdered,

45:56.110 --> 45:58.570
they saw Young Master Shi
leaving in a hurry.

45:58.710 --> 45:59.510
Grandfather,

45:59.920 --> 46:01.130
this is true.

46:01.560 --> 46:03.850
I saw Shi kill Jin with my own eyes.

46:04.630 --> 46:05.760
He also injured me.

46:07.320 --> 46:08.520
I fought desperately

46:08.670 --> 46:10.350
to protect this ring.

46:11.230 --> 46:12.030
Grandfather,

46:13.020 --> 46:14.220
now that you're back,

46:15.250 --> 46:17.080
you must avenge Jin's death.

46:18.030 --> 46:19.030
Jin was murdered.

46:19.760 --> 46:22.850
The position of clan leader
has fallen into Zheng Shi's hands.

46:22.850 --> 46:23.910
In our generation,

46:24.670 --> 46:26.470
there is no one who can rival him.

46:27.800 --> 46:28.510
If...

46:30.110 --> 46:32.550
If I had Jin's talent,

46:34.370 --> 46:36.880
I could surely
share your burden, Grandfather.

46:36.880 --> 46:37.480
Master,

46:38.840 --> 46:39.880
we absolutely can not

46:39.880 --> 46:41.540
let that fratricide murderer

46:41.620 --> 46:43.480
take the position of clan leader.

46:44.110 --> 46:46.440
Third Young Master,
please do not belittle yourself.

46:46.440 --> 46:48.530
After all, you are Master's grandson.

46:48.530 --> 46:49.590
In terms of talent,

46:49.600 --> 46:52.330
I don't think
you are any inferior to anyone else.

46:54.230 --> 46:55.150
Grandfather!

46:56.630 --> 46:58.230
I am willing to be your blade,

46:58.280 --> 47:00.510
seize the position of clan leader for you,

47:00.510 --> 47:02.230
and let Jin rest in peace.

47:02.800 --> 47:04.360
I only beg you, Grandfather,

47:04.360 --> 47:05.710
to grant me a chance.

47:07.280 --> 47:08.590
Jin was murdered.

47:10.280 --> 47:11.740
Who else knows about this?

47:11.810 --> 47:13.270
When the Eldest Young Master was murdered,

47:13.270 --> 47:15.150
you still hadn't returned, Master.

47:15.150 --> 47:17.130
I was worried
that the Zheng family might fall

47:17.130 --> 47:18.660
into chaos without a leader,

47:18.660 --> 47:20.170
so I kept the news confidential long ago.

47:20.170 --> 47:21.850
No one will leak it for sure.

47:22.400 --> 47:24.290
Inform all the clan members

47:25.280 --> 47:26.510
that I have returned,

47:27.230 --> 47:28.830
and the clan leader election

47:28.990 --> 47:30.920
will be moved up and held tomorrow.

47:31.380 --> 47:32.100
Also,

47:32.350 --> 47:34.270
lock down the city gates immediately.

47:34.270 --> 47:35.410
Before the election,

47:35.410 --> 47:37.150
no suspicious persons are
allowed in or out.

47:37.150 --> 47:39.070
Everyone, stay on high alert.

47:39.550 --> 47:40.070
Yes.

47:44.770 --> 47:46.730
I want Nine Cities

47:48.910 --> 47:50.950
to lose Jing City forever.

47:58.120 --> 48:00.400
I know everyone has been busy lately.

48:00.510 --> 48:02.310
I had nothing to do at home alone,

48:02.710 --> 48:04.560
so I made some Ling'an wontons.

48:05.000 --> 48:06.730
Enjoy them while they're warm.

48:07.480 --> 48:08.280
Give it a try.

48:12.100 --> 48:12.960
Have some more.

48:18.520 --> 48:19.520
Fourth Lady.

48:20.110 --> 48:21.160
Are you

48:21.330 --> 48:22.690
not used to this food?

48:25.630 --> 48:26.260
Suyin,

48:26.730 --> 48:29.230
do you still have the pastries
you made for me last time?

48:29.230 --> 48:29.770
Yes.

48:34.070 --> 48:35.070
Try this one.

48:36.820 --> 48:37.860
Give me one, too.

48:40.260 --> 48:40.900
How is it?

48:45.640 --> 48:46.690
So you mean

48:47.110 --> 48:48.640
the Zheng Residence only has

48:48.640 --> 48:50.170
a small batch of munitions.

48:50.360 --> 48:51.680
The bulk of it is

48:51.700 --> 48:53.160
stored outside Jing City.

48:53.920 --> 48:54.890
It's an insane amount.

48:54.890 --> 48:56.380
They cover more than half a hill.

48:56.380 --> 48:57.310
If they explode,

48:57.330 --> 48:59.590
the entire Jing City would be destroyed.

49:00.480 --> 49:01.150
Liu Mu,

49:01.920 --> 49:02.770
let's go

49:02.800 --> 49:04.000
out of the city again.

49:04.080 --> 49:05.990
Those munitions can't remain there.

49:05.990 --> 49:07.170
We must thoroughly get rid of them.

49:07.170 --> 49:07.830
No problem.

49:08.840 --> 49:09.700
Your Excellency,

49:09.700 --> 49:10.780
I'm going with you.

49:13.800 --> 49:15.130
You'd better stay here.

49:15.480 --> 49:17.360
Now that you are the gate commander
of Jing City,

49:17.360 --> 49:18.960
you should stay in Jing City.

49:20.360 --> 49:21.760
As for the matters outside the city,

49:21.760 --> 49:22.960
just leave them to me.

49:24.480 --> 49:26.090
Then I will go with you.

49:26.460 --> 49:27.590
With me by your side,

49:27.590 --> 49:30.120
it will be easier for you
to get out of the city.

49:32.060 --> 49:32.750
All right.

49:34.320 --> 49:35.650
Then Suyin and Tian Xing

49:35.730 --> 49:36.790
will stay with you,

49:36.800 --> 49:38.150
so you can look after each other.

49:38.150 --> 49:40.150
Just rest assured and leave it to me.

49:40.900 --> 49:41.730
Then you

49:41.970 --> 49:43.090
must be careful.

49:51.230 --> 49:52.280
Stay safe.

49:52.840 --> 49:53.550
You, too.

49:54.550 --> 49:55.110
Let's go.

49:55.130 --> 49:55.680
Go.

50:07.250 --> 50:07.850
Fan Yun.

50:10.530 --> 50:11.700
Z-Zheng Shi?

50:12.320 --> 50:13.110
You...

50:13.130 --> 50:14.260
Why are you here?

50:15.400 --> 50:18.660
Didn't we agree
that you wouldn't go beyond the courtyard?

50:19.230 --> 50:20.540
But in Jing City,

50:21.440 --> 50:22.410
everywhere is

50:22.800 --> 50:24.530
like your courtyard, isn't it?

50:58.920 --> 50:59.360
Oh...

51:01.840 --> 51:02.390
You...

51:03.250 --> 51:04.180
You got wounded.

51:06.560 --> 51:07.230
It's fine.
